    new "趁她工作时去杰克逊汉堡店买个汉堡，并主动提出帮她忙。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:17
    old "Doing good."
    new "干得不错。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:19
    old "Is anything wrong?"
    new "有什么问题吗？"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:36
    old "Sure, that's no problem."
    new "当然，没问题。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:43
    old "Ass, gas, or grass, lady."
    new "屁股、汽油还是大麻，女士。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:48
    old "Okay then."
    new "那好吧。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:55
    old "I'm really just more interested in the 'ass' part"
    new "其实我更感兴趣的是“屁股”那部分"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:99
    old "Pretty sneaky"
    new "挺狡猾的"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:103
    old "I wouldn't ever kick you out"
    new "我才不会赶你走呢"

